  "text": "It is shown [CITATION_1] that under some stability conditions and after an initial period of relaxation, the simplest LBGK collision with overrelaxation [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] provides second order accurate approximation for the macroscopic transport equation with viscosity proportional to δt(1 − β)/β.",
